{"title":"开春的土地（外二首）","authors":["江健"],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":1,"day":12}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"开春的土地（外二首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江健"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你站在地头的时候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以雁阵的队列"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凌空向你进逼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿色的原野"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泥土散发出荞麦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"淡淡的香味"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时间的堤坝怎能挡住流水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桃花在少女的脸颊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"次第开放"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使你的爱情热烈　辽远"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一大片一大片"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朴素的愿望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"随风撒向土地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阳光的种子　默默扬穗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仿佛黎明的乐曲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天，流注在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你心灵的每一寸土地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这时，妻子们的肢体"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开遍了美丽的绿桑叶子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而宁静的村庄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炊烟袅袅升起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"暮秋风景"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"此刻　在庄园的上空"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大雁灰色的影子一掠而过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"空旷的地头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我依然看见"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"采菊南山下的陶氏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悠然走过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耧铃使我想起劳动的农民"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"霜打的土地　太阳闪耀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在庄园与庄园之间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我见到了遍地生长的葵花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"季节的悬崖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"树叶飘零"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"少女的爱情依然斩钉截铁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风息时"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一支闪亮的铧犁切开了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冬播的土地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你破冰而来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我听见了冰碎裂的声音"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鱼的声音"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"远处渔歌子的声音"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我站在河岸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干裂的心中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有水流拍响的声音"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你裂空而来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我看见鸟掠过南方的翅膀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风的翅膀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"原野上绿色的树的翅膀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我站在三月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身体轻如蝴蝶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深入春天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我触摸到你的柔情与温馨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我相信在凛冽的寒冬过后"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鱼游动的样子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和鸟飞翔的样子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都是生命的姿态"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而我的手在溶溶春色中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长成了五支花蕾＊"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}